\f1\fs24 The Spiritual Exercises\
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Jesuits sometimes refer to themselves as \'93men of the exercises\'94\
\ls6\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 The exercises demand total intellectual, emotional and spiritual engagement. Accordingly, they monopolize focus and energy for their thirty-day duration.\
\ls6\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Loyola purged distractions in order to free time and psychic space, so each recruit is left alone with himself\
\ls6\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Over the course of a month, trainees deconstruct themselves in order to erect solid personal foundations of self-awareness, ingenuity, heroism and love\
\ls6\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 The enemy of our human nature, our disordered affections, our false lovers\
\ls6\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \'93taking stock of who I am, where I want to go, and what is holding me back\'94\
\ls6\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Jesuits achieved what we today call ingenuity \'97 a mix of adaptability, daring, speed, and good judgement \'97 only by first cultivating the attitude he called \'93indifference\'94\
\ls6\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \'93Inordinate attachments\'94 fog one\'92s vision\
\ls6\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Only by becoming indifferent \'97 free of prejudices and attachments and therefore free to choose any course of action \'97 do recruits become strategically flexible\
\ls6\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 The indifferent Jesuit liberates himself to choose strategies driven by one motive only: achieving his long term goal of serving God by helping souls\
\ls6\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 A heroic Jesuit is as much coiled to jump at whats next yet poised to act strategically, both simultaneously at equilibrium\
\ls6\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \'93Love ought to manifest itself more by deeds than by words\'94\
\ls6\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \'93shared humanity means something\'94\
\ls6\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 The exercises were especially designed for those immersed in a busy lifestyle in an ever-changing world\'85 examens work for busy people\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading20\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
