\f2\fs20 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 The Whole World Becomes Our House\
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Ingenuity is the readiness to cross the world at a moment\'92s notice in full-hearted pursuit of a good opportunity, as Xavier was about to do. It is the willingness to work without a script and to dream up imaginative new approaches to problems that have stymied others.\
\ls7\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Indifference frees Jesuits from prejudices, attachments, fears, and narrow-mindedness that can block the enthusiastic pursuit of new ideas and opportunities\
\ls7\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Instead of running to embrace the world, the pioneers of religious life had mostly headed fast in the other direction, each sheltered like-minded souls who left behind worldly pursuits for monastic study, prayer, and manual labor\
\ls7\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Benedictine monks vow \'93stability\'94 to live their remaining years in the monastic house of which they joined\
\ls7\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 The Jesuits vowed to find God in the world rather than behind walls\
\ls7\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \'93contemplative in action\'94 wield strategies for maintaining focus and composure in a busy lifestlye\
\ls7\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 When in Asia, De Nobili had rich arguments in ammuntion from sources spanning everything from Roman mythology to Jesus Christ to St. Augustine to the Hindu laws of Manu. His obscure references likely sent leading theologians scurrying to their concordances in befuddlement\
\ls7\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \'93where does one draw the line between interfaith dialogue and aggressive proselytization\
\ls7\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs24 \cf3 proselytize
\f1\b0 \cf0  \'97 convert or attempt to convert (someone) from one religion, belief, or opinion to another.\
\ls7\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 The Jesuits and the exercises prepare men to be free to do whatever the situation calls for \'97 give an order, take an order or chart his own course; casting the spirit of indifference into a whole new light\
\ls7\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 The Jesuits were decidedly global, with authority radiating from a strong hub to many spokes, lavishly delegating to whoever could make the best informed, fastest decisions in the field.\
\ls7\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \'93The confidence Loyola showed to those to whom he was entrusting some important affair, by giving them complete freedom, and credit, and allowing them authority to act according to the capacity and talent of each one\
\ls7\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \'93Cut your suit according to your cloth; only let us know how you have acted\'94\
\ls7\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Speed, innovation and global focus happen only when lots of delegated authority sits alongside lots of centralized authority\'85a tightly centralized authority lay beside wide-open self-initiative \
\ls7\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Take an order today, chart a course tomorrow \'97 just as long as we are headed where we need to go\
\ls7\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Those who come to the table with a strong understanding of their non-negotiables can pounce instinctively on opportunities that suit their broader objectives\
\ls7\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \cf2 de Nobili took enormous personal risks while doing difficult, often lonely work and few people can detach themselves from fear with that level off effectiveness\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading20\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0
\f2\fs20 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Refuse No Talent Nor Any Man of Quality\
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 The cofounders were determined to enshrine love as a cornerstone in their fledgling company\
\ls8\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs24 \cf3 fledgling
\f1\b0 \cf0  \'97 a person or organization that is immature, inexperienced, or underdeveloped.\
\ls8\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Loving their superiors, their peers, their subordinates, their enemies, an those they served changed not only the way the Jesuits looked at others, but what they saw. Their vision became more acute, their eyes on talent opened to talent and potential\
\ls8\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 They saw human talent and potential where others didn\'92t even look for it. Love was the guiding vision that enabled them to do so\
\ls8\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \'93No perceives others accurately without first achieving healthy self-regard\'94\
\ls8\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \'93To those who were still children in virtue, Ignatius gave milk; but to those who were more advanced, bread with crust; while he treated the perfect more rigorously still, in order to make them run at full speed towards perfection\'94\
\ls8\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \cf2 Love-driven leaders hunger to see latent potential blossom and to help it happen, they engender trust, provide support and encouragement, uncover potential, and set high standards.\
\ls8\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 When love-driven leadership takes root on a widespread basis, it energizes performances and creates unique bonds of team unity. \
\ls8\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Jesuits were well-educated, talented, ambitious and opinionated men\
\ls8\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Out basic worldview \'97 our vision of humanity \'97 will inevitably affect our day-to-day dealings\
\ls8\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \cf2 Minimal \'93teamwork\'94 standards pale when compared with the behaviors of unified, love-driven teams. Unlike energy-sapping workplaces riddled with backstabbing and second-guessing, environments of greater love than fear GENERATE energy.\cf0 \
\ls8\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Those who would rather help peers succeed than watch them fail are creating environments of greater love than fear\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading20\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0
\f2\fs20 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 An Uninterrupted Life of Heroic Deeds\
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 How to move from cynical, going-through-the-motions performance to motivated, even heroic performance\
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl2
\f2\fs20 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Invite recruits to turn a corporate aspiration into a personal mission\
\ls9\ilvl2
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Create a company culture that stresses heroism, modeling the virtue themselves\
\ls9\ilvl2
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Give each person the opportunity to enlarge himself by contributing meaningfully to an enterprise greater than his own interests\
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Personal commitment needs support and constant reinforcement from the top\
\ls9\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \'93The society wants men who are as accomplished as possible in every discipline that helps it in its purpose. Can you become a good logician? Then become one! A good theologian? Then become one!\'85and do not be satisfied with doing it half-way.\'94\
\ls9\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \'93You cannot motivate anyone to do a good job unless he has a good job to do\'94\
\ls9\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \cf2 A restless, countercultural instinct to keep challenging the status quo was built into Jesuit heroism. The built-in energy of the magis pointed always toward some better approach to the problem at hand or some worthier challenge to tackle. The Jesuit\'92s self-reflective habits denied them the luxury of \'93just going with the flow,\'94 so that they may \'93live with one foot raised.\'94\cf0 \
\ls9\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \'93We are working to lay the foundations of houses which will last as long as the world endures\'94\
\ls9\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \cf2 The candidates they sought were spiritually engaged, totally committed, intellectually superior, capable of debating theology in Ladin with the leading Protestant theologians and of explaining the same ideas in the vernacular to peasant children, ready to cross the globe on forty-eight hour\'92s notice, equally comfortable working in university lecture halls as in plague hospitals, ready to take orders or design their own strategies.\
\ls9\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \cf2 The real leadership comes from the trenches\cf0 \
\ls9\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \'93Jesuit leaders exhibited the risk tolerance, creativity, and aggressiveness to capitalize on opportunities\'94\
\ls9\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 The network was built from the bottom up, not visioned top-down. Insofar as there was an overarching vision, it was a decidedly retail one \'97 \'93the teachers should be outstanding.\'94 And so so they ended up with the best network of schools in the world, one outstanding teacher at a time.\
\ls9\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 heroism \'97 percolates bottom up, from magis-driven leaders. Such heroism can\'92t be bought, bartered, manipulated, or forced. It\'92s freely passed along by self-motivated individuals enthused about their work.\
\ls9\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Successful leaders spend their time creating environments where individuals will choose heroism as a way of working and living \
\ls9\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Risk-taking comes easier to the edgy, nothing-to-lose start-up than to the well-established, everything-to-lose mainstream player\
\ls9\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Superbly educated in core disciplines, yet driven through indifference to seize new intellectual current, Jesuits married traditional scholastic disciplines and the best ideas of progressive humanism in their schools\
\ls9\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \cf2 Magis-driven leadership involves bold imagination and the desire to take bold chances.\
\ls9\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Jesuits prospered most when they mustered all the heroism and ingenuity they could to continue their high-wire acts. \
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading20\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0
\f2\fs20 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Exceptional Daring Was Essential\
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Success breeds complacency \
\ls10\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \cf2 Continued focus on what lies ahead and on what more ambitious goals can be achieved, remains the only reliable way to ensure that important parts of the vision and mission remain vital and aren\'92t overlooked \'97 or discarded altogether.\cf0 \
\ls10\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs24 \cf4 ostentation
\f1\b0 \cf0  \'97 pretentious and vulgar display, especially of wealth and luxury, intended to impress or attract notice\
\ls10\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f0\b\fs24 \cf4 ignominious
\f1\b0 \cf0  - deserving or causing public disgrace or shame\
\ls10\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \cf2 Great results emerge one motivated individual at a time. \
\ls10\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Magis-driven leadership inevitably leads to heroism\
\ls10\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \cf2 Instead of waiting for golden opportunities, they find the gold in the opportunities at hand. Heros lift themselves up and make themselves greater by pursuing something greater than their own self-interest.\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading20\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl0
\f2\fs20 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 The Way We Do Things\
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 The link between self-awareness and ingenuity, stability and change epitomizes self-reinforcing principles in action.\
\ls11\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 An entrenched culture can make implementing new and different strategies very difficult\
\ls11\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 A strong corporate culture:\
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl2
\f2\fs20 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 has tangible day to day employee behavior\
\ls11\ilvl2
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 is strategically appropriate \
\ls11\ilvl2
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 promotes adaptability and doesn\'92t block it\
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \cf2 Successful cultures tap the motivating power of deeply held beliefs\cf0 \
\ls11\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 The critical importance of creating tangible mechanisms aligned to preserve the core and simulate progress\
\ls11\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Well-defined anchoring goals and values enable ambitious, even drastic innovation and adaptability\
\ls11\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 By clearly demarcating the boundaries he wouldn\'92t cross, de Nobili understood the playing field within which he could experiment with confidence \
\ls11\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Creative constraints breed creativity\
\ls11\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \cf2 Those who don\'92t know their nonnegotiable goals and values become loose canons \'97 they have plenty of firepower but no clear target\
\ls11\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Jesuit recruits first inventoried personal weaknesses and change-blocking \'93inordinate attachments\'94\
\ls11\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \'93Knowing themselves as loved transformed the way they looked at others. Because they were anchored by an appreciation of their own dignity, they developed an appreciation of the aspirations, potential and dignity of others.\'94\
\ls11\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Loyola had understood that Jesuit immersed in a complex world would find themselves confronted with difficult choices.\
\ls11\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \'93No one will successfully honor life principles during EVERY moment of a life lived in vigorous pursuit of those principles.\'94\
\ls11\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Loyola wanted recruits to mull a decision over from different angles, including from the sobering perspectives of one\'92s deathbed.\
\ls11\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Men need to realize that their whole lives can be the example of leadership, whether at the end its considered a success or failure\
\ls11\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \cf2 With personal risk comes missteps, but not to take risks is to shrink from leadership and dissipate one\'92s potential.\
\ls11\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 Profound personal transformation takes place over a lifetime: from youth to old age, through changes in occupation, changes in relationships, and changes in life circumstances. What gives give life its wholeness and integrity was his lifelong commitment to a set of goals and values.\
\ls11\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \cf2 Whether these life principles are discovered early or late in life, the commitment to measure life choices against them is crucial. By this process, life is transformed from a succession of random episodes to something whole, a life with integrity.\cf0 \
\ls11\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 \'93Jesuits learn best by teaching others\'94\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading20\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls12\ilvl0
